    <div id="content" role="main">
        <!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="content" -->

        <h1>Using XE Registration</h1>
        <h2>Page Sections:</h2>
        <ul id="jump-menu">
            <li><a href="#overview" title="Overview of XE Registration">Overview</a></li>
            <li><a href="#search-register" title="Search and Register Step Anchor">Search and Register</a></li>
            <li><a href="#enter-crn" title="Enter CRN Step Anchor">Enter CRN</a></li>
            <li><a href="#errors" title="Errors Anchor">Error Messages</a></li>
            <li><a href="#linked-courses" title="Link Courses Anchor">Linked Courses</a></li>
            <li><a href="#credit-hours" title="Changing Number of Credit Hours Anchor">Changing Number of Credit Hours</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div id="overview" class="section">
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>Banner XE is a new look and feel for registration processes at UIC. The images and information below provide a step by step process to register for classes. Banner XE allows for greater search capabilities for classes and more streamlined registration. Students can call our Registration Help Line at 312-996-8600 during business hours with questions.</p>
            <div class="image-wrapper">
                <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-1.jpg" title="Full Size image of BANNER XE home page"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-1.jpg" alt="Screen shot of BANNER XE home page" /> <br/>Larger</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="search-register" class="section">
            <h2>Search and Register</h2>
            <p>To search and register for classes, follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>From the home page, click on "Register for Classes"<br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-2.jpg" title="Full Size image of BANNER XE home page"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-2.jpg" alt="Screen shot of BANNER XE home page" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Select the term open for registration and click "Continue"<br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-3.jpg" title="Full Size image of selecting a term for registration screen shot"><img class="md" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-3.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Selecting a term for Registration" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Click the blank box next to "Subject" to scroll through the subjects or type in the desired subject. Click "Search".<br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-4.jpg" title="Full size image of search criteria form screen shot"><img class="md" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-4.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Search Criteria form for Registration" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                   You can also type the course number. For example, if looking for "BA 190", Business Administration goes in Subject field and 190 in Course Number field. <br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-5.jpg" title="Full size image of Search criteria form with autocomplete field screen shot"><img class="md" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-5.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Search Criteria form with autocompleted subject field for Registration" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-6.jpg" title="Full size image of completed Search Criteria form screen shot"><img class="md" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-6.jpg" alt="Screen shot of completed Search Criteria form for Registration" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Look through the results using the arrows on the bottom left, and click "Add" next to the course you want.<br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-7.jpg" title="Full size image of Course listings screen shot"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-7.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Course Listings after a search" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                   The added course will be posted under Summary, and you will click "Submit".<br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-8.jpg" title="Full size image of Course listings with summary screen shot"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-8.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Course listings after form submission with summary view" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                   If successful, the status will change from "Pending" to "Registered" under Status.<br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-10.jpg" title="Full size image of course listing with registered status in summary screen shot"><img class="md" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-10.jpg" alt="Screen shot of course listing with registered status in summary" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Optional:</strong> To remove a course, click the drop down arrow under "Action", select "Web Drop Course", and click "Submit".<br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-11.jpg" title="Full size image of removing a course from summary view screen shot"><img class="md" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-11.jpg" alt="Screen shot exposed dropwdown in summary in order to remove a course" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div id="enter-crn" class="section">
            <h2>Enter CRN</h2>
            <p>To search for courses by CRN, follow this step:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>If you know the CRNs of your courses, go to "Enter CRNs" tab, and type in the CRNs. Click "Add to Summary" and then "Submit".
                    <br/>
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-12.jpg" title="Full size image of Enter CRN form screen shot"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-12.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Enter CRN form" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div id="errors" class="section">
            <h2>Error Messages</h2>
            <p>If unsuccessful while trying to add or remove a course(s), error message(s) will appear at the top and status will say "Errors Preventing Registration". Contact the course department if it is a "Departmental Approval Required" or "Class Restriction" or "College Restriction" error message. If "Linked Course Error" appears, continue reading about <a href="#linked-courses" title="">linked courses</a>.</p>
            <div class="image-wrapper">
                <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-13.jpg" title="Full size image of error messages populated"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-13.jpg" alt="Screen shot of error messages being displayed on a page" /> <br/>Larger</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="linked-courses" class="section">
            <h2>Linked Courses</h2>
            <p>To properly register for linked courses, follow these stesp:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>While on the register for classes page, select "View Linked". Keep in mind that the first letter under section has to match. Example: "AL1" goes with "AD4".
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-14.jpg" title="Full size image of register for classes screen shot"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-14.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Register for Classes" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li>Scroll through the options. Click "Add All" and then click "Submit".
                    <div class="image-wrapper">
                        <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-15.jpg" title="Full size of image of linked courses being added"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-15.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Linked courses being added by pressing add all button" /> <br/>Larger</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div id="credit-hours" class="section">
            <h2>Changing Number of Credit Hours</h2>
            <p>Changing the number of credit hours for a course can be requested. If approved, you follow these steps to make the changes for your account:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>From the home page, click the "Schedule and Options" tab.</li>
                <li>Under "Hours", click the underlined number next to the course.</li>
                <li>Once the text field appears, proceed to change to the approved number of hours.</li>
                <li>Finally, click "Submit" at the bottom right.</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="image-wrapper">
                <a href="/assets/images/xe-registration-18.jpg" title="Full size image of Schedule and options screen shot"><img class="lg" src="/assets/images/xe-registration-18.jpg" alt="Screen shot of Schedule and Options page with red boxes pointing to the areas where the 4 steps are to be conducted." /> <br/>Larger</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- InstanceEndEditable -->
